🚨 Recent college grads face tough job prospects. With AI automating entry-level work &amp; uncertainty over tariffs, hiring growth has plunged from 7.3% to just 0.6%.

“Companies are in a wait-and-see mode,” says career coach Beth Hendler-Grunt.
